                            the built-in tailwind integration for base-ui makes
                            use of this feature through its initTailwind()
                            function. so when you call initTailwind, it
                            initializes an init hook that applies the styles you
                            made to an element. but keep in mind that if you
                            don't need tailwind, you can safely delete the
                            integration.
                        </p>

                        <div class="p-3"></div>

